{"tid":1957742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位黃衛兵停止批鬥","createTime":"2020-04-04T06:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T06:05:10.000Z","uid":5590,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"574e404f905798619151fafa70d6037ebdfaeb7a","tid":1957742,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:28:24.000Z","msg":"從一開始我地上街叫口號就係手足，變到今日你三餐唔食黃店，每日做唔足任務就唔係黃，仲經常講「XXX都冇，黃極都有限啦」<br />\n呢種鬥黃，批鬥唔夠黃的風氣會將門檻一直提高，排斥自己人。<br />\n<br />\n今日的連登同大陸小粉紅一樣，我認為咁係另類加速主義，加速大眾對黃的厭惡<br />\n<br />\n批鬥黃的人唔夠黃，只會減少自己人<br />\n與其將黃的人變得更黃，不如將藍的變黃<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家停止批鬥</span>"},{"pid":"65183d343b309fdf46048013c95db39472d7e37d","tid":1957742,"uid":265839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:29:39.000Z","msg":"黃包容，藍消滅<br />\n不割蓆不批鬥"},{"pid":"95cf90c8de112c67ac3e383285fc47f52127335d","tid":1957742,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcce6aff9ecd3acdcea73c14eea91b2c62bf09e","tid":1957742,"uid":177213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:37:32.000Z","msg":"兒登仔理撚得你<br />\n老母係藍自動當埋你係藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最鍾意玩批鬥"},{"pid":"d8d0812a8e34cd7e297efad14de167f7d012da0f","tid":1957742,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:41:28.000Z","msg":"請多啲宣傳呢句:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">批鬥手足者皆偽黃</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4d2624b26eb43e00d97dfa870345017d9cee8c","tid":1957742,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:42:46.000Z","msg":"叫人黃衛兵你都唔好得去邊"},{"pid":"d64f03ae4597b29ac2bdf9c375eea1e15477ee83","tid":1957742,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"